COMMITMENT OF C.H., et al., Appellants Supreme Court of Indiana. April 30, 2019 Denied. Vaidik, C.J., Riley, J., Kirsch, J.

All Justices concur, except Rush, C.J., and Slaughter, J., who vote to grant transfer, believing Commissioner Kelly M. Scanlan lacked authority to enter judgment and that the commitment order is thus void.
